name: Diary of the Broken - S3 Free Claim

metadata.name: With You; My Eternity #1/7
metadata.description:
Sharing my eternity with you,  
Is a dream that's pure and true,  
A bond that lasts beyond the blue,  
Our love forever strong and new.  
With every breath that I take,  
I'll cherish you, my love, for eternity's sake,  
With every beat of my heart,  
I'll love you till death do us part.
